data.description: SOLD AS IS.   Nice Home in The Douglasville Community Near Schools, Shopping and Dinning.     First Time Home Buyer or Investor Opportunity!!! Great Price!!! Wont last long!!!    This Home features 3 Bedrooms 2 Full Bathrooms with a lower Terrace/Basement Level. Open concept Floor plan, Laminate Hardwood Floors throughout. Spacious bedrooms with Huge Private Backyard with unlimited potential. Fairly NEW HVAC, HOT WATER HEATER. WASHER/DRYER & REFRIGERATOR STAYS WITH HOME.  Owner Occupied please allow one hour prior to showing request for approval.   Appointments Only.
